{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"**Root cause:** The DSL uses `run` as the config key for script steps (e.g., `run = \"go test ./... 2\u003e\u00261\"`), but both the backend and frontend were looking for `command`/`script` instead.","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:12:54.556590487Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:12:54.55660764Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"**Backend fix** (`handler.go:1184-1193`): Changed `step.Config[\"command\"]` and `step.Config[\"script\"]` lookups to `step.Config[\"run\"]`. For inline commands (not file references), `resolveStepContent` will fail to read them as files, and the handler falls back to returning the raw string.","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:12:54.556612559Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:12:54.556624281Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"**Frontend fix** (`project_detail.html:263`): Changed the config display filter from `'command'`/`'script'` to `'run'` so that script step commands are shown in the drawer metadata.","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:12:54.55662905Z"}
